 4584, \"end\": 4617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FINA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Swimming Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FINA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FINA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(formerly FINA\", \"from\": 4618, \"to\": 4632}, {\"ngram\": \"World Aquatics\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4661}, {\"ngram\": \"those swim caps\", \"from\": 4670, \"to\": 4685}, {\"ngram\": \"the natural form\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4733}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 4737, \"to\": 4745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This decision was made by the governing body, because, to their \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cbest knowledge, the athletes competing at the international events never used, neither require to use, caps of such size and configuration,\\\"according to the AP.\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4987, \"end\": 4989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4412892539108295e-22, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This decision\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4776}, {\"ngram\": \"the governing body\", \"from\": 4789, \"to\": 4807}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cbest knowledge\", \"from\": 4821, \"to\": 4844}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 4846, \"to\": 4858}, {\"ngram\": \"the international events\", \"from\": 4872, \"to\": 4896}, {\"ngram\": \"caps\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 4937}, {\"ngram\": \"such size\", \"from\": 4941, \"to\": 4950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simply put, Black hair is not allowed to be Black hair.\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Black hair\", \"from\": 5004, \"to\": 5014}, {\"ngram\": \"Black hair\", \"from\": 5036, \"to\": 5046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, this decision revealed just how limited the scope of who was historically welcomed to swim in public.\\u00c2 The ban was met with backlash from athletes like Black British swimmer Alice Dearing, whotold The Guardian, \\\"Back in the 1960s, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve seen those images of a black woman in a swimming pool and a white man pouring acid into it while she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s there.\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5216, \"end\": 5229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_British_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Black British\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_British_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_British_people\"}, {\"begin\": 5238, \"end\": 5251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Dearing\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alice Dearing\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Dearing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Dearing\"}, {\"begin\": 5261, \"end\": 5273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Guardian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.175975758620424e-30, \"text\": \"The Guardian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Guardian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Guardian\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 5064, \"to\": 5077}, {\"ngram\": \"just how limited the scope\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5113}, {\"ngram\": \"public\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5164}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 5165, \"to\": 5166}, {\"ngram\": \"The ban\", \"from\": 5167, \"to\": 5174}, {\"ngram\": \"backlash\", \"from\": 5188, \"to\": 5196}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 5202, \"to\": 5210}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1960s\", \"from\": 5284, \"to\": 5293}, {\"ngram\": \"those images\", \"from\": 5307, \"to\": 5319}, {\"ngram\": \"a black woman\", \"from\": 5323, \"to\": 5336}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimming pool\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5355}, {\"ngram\": \"a white man\", \"from\": 5360, \"to\": 5371}, {\"ngram\": \"acid\", \"from\": 5380, \"to\": 5384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And there were instances where Black people were just outright banned from pools.\", \"from\": 5414, \"to\": 5495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instances\", \"from\": 5429, \"to\": 5438}, {\"ngram\": \"Black people\", \"from\": 5445, \"to\": 5457}, {\"ngram\": \"pools\", \"from\": 5489, \"to\": 5494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not really a surprise that we get to 2020 or the 21st century and we see these issues occurring and there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a lack of Black people in swimming, because it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just been decades and decades of historical and cultural racism.\\\"\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"not really a surprise\", \"from\": 5506, \"to\": 5527}, {\"ngram\": \"the 21st century\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5567}, {\"ngram\": \"these issues\", \"from\": 5579, \"to\": 5591}, {\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a lack\", \"from\": 5606, \"to\": 5622}, {\"ngram\": \"Black people\", \"from\": 5626, \"to\": 5638}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 5642, \"to\": 5650}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 5660, \"to\": 5666}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5684}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5696}, {\"ngram\": \"historical and cultural racism\", \"from\": 5700, \"to\": 5730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fewer Black swimmers (and competitive swimmers at that) meant that World Aquatics \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 which is based in Switzerland where the Black population is in the minority andfaces racism\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 based their decision on the majority of swimmers with thinner hair that would lay flatter on the head, not on Black hair textures.\\u00c2 Soul Capstated,\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cTraditional swimming caps often do not accommodate these hair types, hindering participation.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Fortunately, the decision to ban the caps wasreversedin 2022 after it went under a year of review and discussion with the cap's creators.\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 6303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5838, \"end\": 5849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.604851657752782e-12, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fewer Black swimmers\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5754}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive swimmers\", \"from\": 5760, \"to\": 5780}, {\"ngram\": \"World Aquatics \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 5801, \"to\": 5819}, {\"ngram\": \"the Black population\", \"from\": 5856, \"to\": 5876}, {\"ngram\": \"the minority andfaces\", \"from\": 5883, \"to\": 5904}, {\"ngram\": \"their decision\", \"from\": 5921, \"to\": 5935}, {\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 5939, \"to\": 5951}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 5963}, {\"ngram\": \"thinner hair\", \"from\": 5969, \"to\": 5981}, {\"ngram\": \"flatter\", \"from\": 5997, \"to\": 6004}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 6008, \"to\": 6016}, {\"ngram\": \"Black hair textures\", \"from\": 6025, \"to\": 6044}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Soul Capstated\", \"from\": 6045, \"to\": 6061}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cTraditional swimming caps\", \"from\": 6062, \"to\": 6092}, {\"ngram\": \"these hair types\", \"from\": 6118, \"to\": 6134}, {\"ngram\": \"participation.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2\", \"from\": 6146, \"to\": 6164}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 6178, \"to\": 6190}, {\"ngram\": \"the caps\", \"from\": 6198, \"to\": 6206}, {\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 6246, \"to\": 6252}, {\"ngram\": \"review\", \"from\": 6256, \"to\": 6262}, {\"ngram\": \"discussion\", \"from\": 6267, \"to\": 6277}, {\"ngram\": \"the cap's creators\", \"from\": 6283, \"to\": 6301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Soul Cap said the approval \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cis a huge step in the right direction \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 bringing inclusive swimwear into competitive swimming, and helping to bring down some of the obstacles that are keeping swimmers away from the sport.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d In a few years, we have come a long way.\", \"from\": 6304, \"to\": 6570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Soul Cap\", \"from\": 6304, \"to\": 6312}, {\"ngram\": \"the approval\", \"from\": 6318, \"to\": 6330}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge step\", \"from\": 6337, \"to\": 6348}, {\"ngram\": \"the right direction\", \"from\": 6352, \"to\": 6371}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive swimming\", \"from\": 6409, \"to\": 6429}, {\"ngram\": \"the obstacles\", \"from\": 6465, \"to\": 6478}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 6496, \"to\": 6504}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 6515, \"to\": 6528}, {\"ngram\": \"a few years\", \"from\": 6532, \"to\": 6543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2024, Simone Manuel, the first Black woman to win an individual gold medal in swimming, created her own foundation to provide equity for communities of color to increase positive swimming experiences.\", \"from\": 6571, \"to\": 6774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6580, \"end\": 6593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Manuel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Manuel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Manuel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Manuel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first Black woman\", \"from\": 6595, \"to\": 6616}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual gold medal\", \"from\": 6624, \"to\": 6648}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\"